    Parameters:
    - params (np.ndarray): Trainable coefficients used by the equation skeleton.
    """
    """Improved version of `equation_v1`.

    Models acceleration of nonlinear harmonic oscillator with polynomial terms up to quartic order,
    including all monomials of degree <= 4 in position and velocity,
    plus nonlinear damping/friction-like effects and periodic forcing components.

    Parameters:
    - x0: Position at time t
    - x1: Velocity at time t
    - params: Trainable coefficients array of length 12

