      params[7] : cubic mixed term x0^2 * x1 coefficient
      params[8] : cubic mixed term x0 * x1^2 coefficient
      params[9] : cubic velocity coefficient
      params[10]: sinusoidal restoring force amplitude
      params[11]: sign(velocity) friction amplitude

    Returns:
