    - Velocity-dependent nonlinear damping terms (including sign-sensitive and exponential forms)
    - Mixed coupling terms between position and velocity
    - Periodic forcing or parametric excitation components dependent on position and velocity

    Parameters:
        x0 (np.ndarray): Position at time t.
        x1 (np.ndarray): Velocity at time t.
        params (np.ndarray): Array of 12 parameters controlling the contribution of each term.

    Returns:
        np.ndarray: Calculated acceleration y.
    """
    
    p = params
    
    y = (
        p[0] * x0                     # linear stiffness term (-k*x)
        + p[1] * x1                   # linear damping term (-c*v)
        + p[2] * x0**3                # cubic stiffness nonlinearity (Duffing type)
        + p[3] * np.abs(x1) * x1      # quadratic velocity-dependent damping (sign-sensitive)
