    including linear and nonlinear stiffness terms, linear and nonlinear damping terms,
    cross coupling polynomial terms, absolute value velocity term for friction-like damping,
    and periodic forcing-like sinusoidal terms.

    Parameters:
        x0 (np.ndarray): Position at time t
        x1 (np.ndarray): Velocity at time t
        params (np.ndarray): Coefficients array with 12 elements

    Returns:
        np.ndarray: Acceleration at time t
    """
    
    (
        c0,   # constant offset acceleration or bias
        c1,   # linear in position - restoring force coefficient (-k/m)
        c2,   # linear in velocity - damping coefficient (-b/m)
        c3,   # quadratic in position - second order stiffness effect
        c4,   # quadratic in velocity - nonlinear damping or drag effect
